<i>adjective</i>: 활발하다 [활발하다], 왕성하다 [왕ː성하다] <i>determiner</i>: 활동적 [활똥적], 적극적 [적끅쩍] <br>
<ul>
<li><i>adjective</i><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>활발하다 [활발하다]</dt><br>
<dd>1. lively; cheerful; outgoing; vigorous</dd><br>
<dd>생기가 있고 힘차다.</dd><br>
<dd>Being full of life and energy.</dd><br>
<dd>2. active; busy</dd><br>
<dd>어떤 일이 많이 이루어지거나 벌어지다.</dd><br>
<dd>Being characterized by vigorous activity or frequent occurrence of a event.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>왕성하다 [왕ː성하다]</dt><br>
<dd>active</dd><br>
<dd>기운이나 세력이 한창 활발하다.</dd><br>
<dd>Energy or power being at its height.</dd><br>
</li>
<li><i>determiner</i><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>활동적 [활똥적]</dt><br>
<dd>1. active; energetic</dd><br>
<dd>몸을 움직여 행동하는.</dd><br>
<dd>Moving one's body to perform some action.</dd><br>
<dd>2. active; energetic</dd><br>
<dd>어떤 일에서 좋은 결과를 거두기 위해 힘쓰는.</dd><br>
<dd>Striving to achieve a good result in a certain task.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>적극적 [적끅쩍]</dt><br>
<dd>active</dd><br>
<dd>어떤 일에 대한 태도에 있어 자발적이고 긍정적인.</dd><br>
<dd>Proactive and positive in attitude toward something.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>